OL,3,CFour to appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FFour men charged after Jewish
OL,8,Fcommunity ambulances were torched in
OL,9,Fnorth-west London are due to appear
OL,10,Fbefore the crown court for the first
OL,11,Ftime on Friday.
OL,13,FThe four ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,14,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,15,Foperating in the Golders Green area,
OL,16,Fwere set on fire in the early hours of
OL,17,FMarch 23, causing gas canisters stored
OL,18,Fin the vehicles to explode and
OL,19,Fresulting in #1 million of damage,
OL,20,Fprosecutors have said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
