OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777114970
OL,3,CFour to appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FHamza Iqbal, 20, Rehan Khan, 19, Judex
OL,8,FAtshatshi, 18, and a 17-year-old boy,
OL,9,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,10,Fare set to appear at the Old Bailey on
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,13,FThey are due to attend for a
OL,14,Fpreliminary hearing before Mrs Justice
OL,15,FCheema-Grubb.
OL,17,FProsecutors have said they believe the
OL,18,Fincident was a targeted attack against
OL,19,Fthe Jewish community.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
