CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777114970
OL,3,CFour to appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FBritish men Iqbal and Khan, from
OL,8,FLeyton, east London, and the 17 year
OL,9,Fold boy, of dual British-Pakistani
OL,10,Fnationality, from Walthamstow, are
OL,11,Fcharged with arson being reckless as
OL,12,Fto whether life would be endangered.
OL,14,FThe trio appeared at Westminster
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on April 4 where
OL,16,Fthey were remanded in custody.
