OL,3,CFour to appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack on Jewish community
OL,5,Cambulances
OL,7,FAtshatshi, a British national from
OL,8,FDagenham, east London, appeared at the
OL,9,Fsame magistrates' court on Saturday,
OL,10,Fcharged with arson with intent to
OL,11,Fdamage property and being reckless as
OL,12,Fto whether life would be endangered.
OL,14,FHe was also remanded in custody.
